---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Service | BingoPlace Limited"
  description="Official Terms of Service for BINGOPLACE LIMITED, governing wholesale trade and supply chain services."
>
  <section class="relative py-32 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background Accents -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-[#050A1A]">
      <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-125 h-125 bg-[#064E3B]/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif mb-6 leading-tight">Terms of <span class="text-[#D4AF37] italic">Service.</span></h1>
        <p class="text-[#D4AF37] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-[10px] font-bold mb-16">Last Updated: May 20, 2026</p>

        <div class="space-y-12 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-light">
          
          <!-- 1. Agreement to Terms -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
            <p>
              By accessing <strong>bingoplaceltd.com</strong> and engaging in wholesale trade with BINGOPLACE LIMITED (Company No. 16998502), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. These terms apply to all visitors, users, and business partners who access or use our services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 2. Business-to-Business (B2B) Nature -->
          <section class="space-y-4 border-l border-[#D4AF37]/30 pl-8 bg-white/5 p-8">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif italic">2. Wholesale & B2B Declaration</h2>
            <p>
              BINGOPLACE LIMITED operates as a <strong>non-specialised wholesale trader (SIC 46900)</strong>. Our services are intended solely for Business-to-Business (B2B) transactions. By placing an order or requesting a quote, you warrant that you are acting in a professional capacity on behalf of a registered business or as a sole trader.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 3. Quotes and Orders -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">3. Quotes, Pricing, and Orders</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>All quotes provided via the website or direct communication are valid for 14 days unless stated otherwise.</li>
              <li>Prices are typically quoted <strong>excluding VAT</strong> and shipping costs, which will be calculated at the point of invoice.</li>
              <li>A contract is only formed once BINGOPLACE LIMITED issues a formal Order Confirmation and has received the agreed-upon deposit or full payment.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <!-- 4. Delivery and Risk -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">4. Delivery and Risk</h2>
            <p>
              While we strive for precision in our logistics, delivery dates are estimates only. Risk of loss or damage to goods passes to the buyer upon delivery to the specified address or upon collection by the buyer's designated carrier.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 5. Returns and Defective Goods -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">5. Returns and Defective Goods</h2>
            <p>
              As a B2B wholesaler, we do not offer a "cooling-off" period. Returns are only accepted for goods that are defective or do not match the agreed specification. Any discrepancies must be reported in writing to our Manchester office within 48 hours of delivery.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 6. Limitation of Liability -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>
              To the maximum extent permitted by the laws of England and Wales, BINGOPLACE LIMITED shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages, including loss of profits or business interruption, arising from the supply of goods. Our total liability is limited to the value of the goods purchased.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 7. Governing Law -->
          <section class="space-y-4">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">7. Governing Law</h2>
            <p>
              These Terms shall be governed and construed in accordance with the <strong>laws of England and Wales</strong>. Any disputes arising from these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in Manchester, UK.
            </p>
          </section>

          <!-- 8. Contact Information -->
          <section class="space-y-6 pt-10">
            <h2 class="text-white text-2xl font-serif">8. Official Contact Details</h2>
            <div class="bg-black/40 p-10 border border-white/5 space-y-2 text-sm">
              <p class="text-white font-bold text-lg mb-4 tracking-wider">BINGOPLACE LIMITED</p>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[#D4AF37] uppercase tracking-widest text-[9px] font-bold mb-2">Registered Office</p>
                  <p>76 King Street</p>
                  <p>Manchester, England</p>
                  <p>M2 4NH</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[#D4AF37] uppercase tracking-widest text-[9px] font-bold mb-2">Registration Details</p>
                  <p>Company Number: 16998502</p>
                  <p>Director: Md Arafat Hossain</p>
                  <p>Email: legal@bingoplaceltd.com</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>

        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 flex items-center gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-[#D4AF37] uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/></svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 bg-white/20 rounded-full"></span>
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[10px] font-bold hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section